{"tid":2101304,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"南韓警方發現首爾市長朴元淳屍體","createTime":"2020-07-09T16:18:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-10T03:19:53.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"22300f41c7e09c9dfcfc69cb34244698c850a5b9","tid":2101304,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T16:18:12.000Z","msg":"南韓警方表示，在叢林山坡發現失蹤的首爾市長朴元淳的屍體。朴元淳的女兒下午報警，指父親在早上10時許留下懷疑遺言後，離開市長官邸，其後手提電話關閉。警方透過手機定位追蹤到朴元淳在城北洞附近一座山，出動150名警員、無人機及警犬搜索。南韓傳媒報道，首爾市政府一名前職員提出刑事訴訟，指控朴元淳涉嫌利用職權進行性騷擾。64歲的朴元淳在2011年首次當選首爾市長，去年贏得第3屆任期，他隸屬執政黨共同民主黨，被視為是2022年總統大選的熱門競選人。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/international/2346303\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Finternational%2F2346303&d=gCjj53haX7oQ0UVj6qLsjpugP7yqsTcUQnBN8ZzcBqk%3D&h=b74f760b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/international/2346303</a>"},{"pid":"10e90c0d83c808e3ac3deec0b52b9a0e1218f2a9","tid":2101304,"uid":19541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T16:18:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0af0c5deb62d240daa5b8aa5daf4bfdcfcda42e7","tid":2101304,"uid":46151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T16:20:52.000Z","msg":"色字頭上一把刀"},{"pid":"22f12270bae35ec1f0ff3776d16f2f1bff7d067b","tid":2101304,"uid":231480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0af0c5deb62d240daa5b8aa5daf4bfdcfcda42e7","tid":2101304,"uid":46151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T16:20:52.000Z","msg":"色字頭上一把刀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T16:22:04.000Z","msg":"但衰11又冇後果"},{"pid":"39f7e6d7d91b5303e6c79da53b7186b69374d792","tid":2101304,"uid":72994,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T16:24:30.000Z","msg":"我真係唔信無內情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5150c25aa692fd391f1ef8087a83b8570b960e1b","tid":2101304,"uid":7